trans-unit.source: Represents a thumbnail image of a document sequence, single document, or single page.
trans-unit.target: 문서 순서, 단일 문서 또는 단일 페이지의 축소판 그림 이미지를 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The XpsThumbnail class has no public constructor.

A reference to an XpsThumbnail is provided through the <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, or <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentSequenceWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods.
trans-unit.target: XpsThumbnail에 대 한 참조를 통해 제공 됩니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentSequenceWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentSequenceWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedDocumentWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.IXpsFixedPageWriter.AddThumbnail%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: It is recommended that if any page in an <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> has a thumbnail, that all pages be specified with thumbnails.
trans-unit.target: 것이 좋습니다 경우 페이지에 <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>축소판 미리 보기를 사용 하 여 모든 페이지 지정 수.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>
